          <img class="img-circle" src="http://www.tenvinilo.com/img/sticker/preview/3055.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="80" height="80">
          <h2><font color="yellow">Shield</font></h2>
          <p>help</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-warning" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
